        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "羟烷基化/烷基化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroxyalkylation/alkylation (HAA) reaction",
        "description": "使用SO₄²⁻/TiO₂固体酸催化剂，在80°C、无溶剂条件下催化2-甲基呋喃与糠醛进行羟烷基化/烷基化反应，生成C15燃料前体FMBM。",
        "text_snippet": "The HAA reaction of 2-MF with furfural to FMBM was performed in a 10 mL thick-walled glass tube heated by an oil bath. Typically, 10–15 mmol 2-MF, 5 mmol furfural and different amounts of S/Ti-T catalyst were mixed to form the reaction solution, which was heated to the specified temperature with a stirring rate of 400 rpm.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation (HDO) reaction",
        "description": "使用Pd/NbOPO₄催化剂，在200°C、5 MPa H₂压力下，于环己烷溶剂中对HAA反应得到的C15燃料前体FMBM进行加氢脱氧反应，生成柴油和喷气燃料范围的C10、C11和C15烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "The HDO reaction of FMBM to alkanes was carried out in a 50 mL autoclave... In a typical reaction, 0.3 g FMBM, a certain amount of Pd/NbOPO4, and 6 mL cyclohexane were transformed into the autoclave. The reaction was then hydrodeoxygenated at the desired temperature (200 ◦C) and H2 pressure (5 MPa) and allowed to react for a certain time (12 h).",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
